TITLE: Implementing Bulk Email Sending Function in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Create a function to send bulk emails using the emailsPost method from the ElasticEmail API. It handles both successful responses and errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elasticemail/elasticemail-ts-axios/blob/master/examples/functions/sendBulkEmails.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const sendBulkEmails = (emailMessageData: EmailMessageData): void => {
  emailsApi.emailsPost(emailMessageData).then((response) => {
      console.log('API called successfully.');
      console.log(response.data);
  }).catch((error) => {
      console.error(error);
  });
};
```

