TITLE: Defining Campaign Object with Recipients and Content
DESCRIPTION: Creates a campaign object with name, recipient list, email content details, and status. The campaign is set to 'Draft' status to postpone sending.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elasticemail/elasticemail-ts-axios/blob/master/examples/functions/addCampaign.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const newCampaign = {
    Name: 'New campaign',
    Recipients: {
      ListNames: ['my list name'],
      SegmentNames: null,
    },
    Content: [{
      From: 'myemail@address.com',
      ReplyTo: 'myemail@address.com',
      TemplateName: 'your_template',
      Subject: 'Hello'
    }],
    Status: 'Draft'
  }; // interface Campaign from '@elasticemail/elasticemail-client-ts-axios'
};
```

